author: The Critical Drinker
description: In a recent interview with The Times, Scarlett Johansson shared her thoughts on her career and the problems she's had with The Male Gaze. I know, right? It's such a drag being one of the most beautiful actresses in Hollywood. But is all as it seems, or is the situation a bit more complicated? Let's find out.
title: Save Us From The Male Gaze!
